3) Add your REPT_XXXX_Extract and REPT_XXXX_Entry to the ADMI_Reporting.properties.template file. An example would be:

	XSALIAS1431=REPT_ESTB_Extract|REPT_ESTB_Extract
	XSALIAS1432=REPT_ESTB_Entry|REPT_ESTB_Entry

